The paper discusses on-device machine learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper also mentions related topics such as online learning, model adaptation, and one/few-shot learning, which are covered in the cs.LG and cs.AI sub-categories. Finally, the paper discusses the use of algorithms and learning theory in on-device learning, which are covered in the cs.DS sub-category.
